task.summary: Created the main class for cache management, cache driver development and cache storage engine connection (even supporting multiple nodes). Added support for local cache storage and external storage using Redis and Memcached as storage engines. Added tests for the created cache drivers, local, Redis and Memcached.

Added support for the SQLite3 cache driver and SQLite3 connection class.
Minor changes:
* Optimized the exceptions import. * Added methods for keys processing "by components". * Added tests for the SQLite3 cache driver.
